        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Holding your weapon aloft, you fill it with divine energy.</p>\n<p>On your next Strike with that weapon before the start of your next turn, you gain a +1 status bonus to the attack roll and the weapon deals an additional die of damage.</p>\n<p>If the weapon has a striking rune, this instead increases the number of dice from the striking rune by 1 (to a maximum of 3 extra weapon dice).</p>\n<p>If the target weapon leaves your possession, weapon surge immediately ends.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Weapon Surge]{Spell Effect: Weapon Surge}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Weapon Surge (Major Striking)]{Spell Effect: Weapon Surge (Major Striking)}</p>"
